plot: Young teenager Momoko Hanasaki is given the power to turn into Wedding Peach, a battle angel charged with protecting love, as well as the Four Sacred Somethings; Four items that hold all love in their balance. Helping Momoko are her friends Yuri and Hinagiku, who have also received the powers of angels, the angel Sir Limone, and Aphrodite, the Goddess of Love.   Written by  Anonymous
